ine-bgcolor:transparent\" dir=\"ltr\" data-darkreader-inline-color data-darkreader-inline-bgcolor><div>Post-CTF Wrap-Up</div></li><li style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;--darkreader-inline-color:var(--darkreader-text-000000, #f0ebe2);--darkreader-inline-bgcolor:transparent\" dir=\"ltr\" data-darkreader-inline-color data-darkreader-inline-bgcolor><div>Planning Checklist</div></li></ul><div><br /></div><div>Happy to send both if useful.</div><div><br />Reply “Send” and I’ll send them over.<br /><br />Sincerely,<br />Noah</div>"
